00:10:32.140 --> 00:10:37.739
like getting rid of all of the things that he was feeling dumb having to decipher. So,

00:10:37.739 --> 00:10:46.299
I think that's a fantastic, fantastic suggestion. Also, when teaching, that is my main takeaway with

00:10:46.299 --> 00:10:50.780
