00:42:54.620 --> 00:42:59.659
you can use Giraffe, you can use React Table, you can use GT. There's all sorts of different

00:42:59.659 --> 00:43:04.379
choices you can even make, even once you're in a specific framework, like R, you can use

00:43:04.379 --> 00:43:09.419
Plotly, you can use Giraffe, you can use React Table, you can use GT. There's all sorts of

00:43:09.580 --> 00:43:13.419
things you can do in a specific framework, like R. Then, like you mentioned, Libby, there's also

00:43:14.219 --> 00:43:18.860
Tableau and Power BI. There's also pure JavaScript, things like D3 and Observable.

00:43:19.419 --> 00:43:27.899
