00:43:46.780 --> 00:43:53.979
for a lot of reasons when we're working with data of various complexity. It's just often

00:43:55.100 --> 00:44:01.100
a really strong approach to build something for a reasonable amount of money, and that's

00:44:01.100 --> 00:44:05.100
really well-designed and works well. So, in terms of picking a stack,

00:44:07.419 --> 00:44:13.820
