00:44:45.899 --> 00:44:52.139
coming up with these beautiful visualizations in, like, an hour, and I'm sure sometimes people took

00:44:52.139 --> 00:44:56.780
more than an hour, but... They do. They do. They took many hours. I don't believe that. Yes,

00:44:57.659 --> 00:45:03.020
but I just, I remember thinking, like, I will never be as good at that as these people, but

00:45:03.020 --> 00:45:09.020
really it was just that I hadn't played around with it enough, you know, and now, oh, let's see,

00:45:09.020 --> 00:45:15.179
12 years into working in R, people come to me all the time with ggplot questions, and I'm like,

